title: The Incal
description:
The Incal. 300+ pages of awesomeness! 

In this edition: The Incal, 
volume 1: The Black Incal
volume 2: The Luminous Incal
volume 3: What Lies Beneath
volume 4: What is Above
volume 5: The Fifth Essence part One: The Dreaming Galaxy
volume 6: The Fifth Essence part Two: Planet Difool

This updated edition includes the extra story "In the Heart of the Impregnable Metabunker".

This book contains the colours used in the original publication of the series by Yves Chaland (book 1), Isabelle Beaumeney-Joanner (books 2,3 and 4) and Zoran Janjetov (books 5 & 6), completely restored and corrected in some minor instances.
